episodes.title: Mary Cosby Explained: Power, Faith, and Cult Allegations
episodes.description:
Mary Cosby’s role on RHOSLC sparked one of the darkest conversations in Bravo history. In this video, we examine the cult allegations, the psychology behind religious authority, and the controversial power structures. #rhoslc #tlc #bravo #marycosby #saltlakecity #megachurch #BritaniBateman

With a special guest to answer questions
